## Update Password

> Request

```http
PATCH <%= config[:version] %>/user/password HTTP/1.1
Host: <%= config[:host] %>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Content-Length: 65

{
    "currentPassword": "Test@123",
    "password": "test@123"
}
```

```shell
curl --location --request PATCH '<%= config[:base_url] %>/user/password' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Authorization: Bearer {access_token}' \
--data-raw '{
    "currentPassword": "Test@123",
    "password": "test@123"
}'
```

```javascript
const axios = require('axios');
let data = JSON.stringify({
  "currentPassword": "Test@123",
  "password": "test@123"
});

let config = {
  method: 'patch',
  maxBodyLength: Infinity,
  url: '<%= config[:base_url] %>/user/password',
  headers: { 
    'Content-Type': 'application/json', 
    'Authorization': 'Bearer {access_token}'
  },
  data : data
};

axios.request(config)
.then((response) => {
  console.log(JSON.stringify(response.data));
})
.catch((error) => {
  console.log(error);
});
```

사용자의 비밀번호를 변경합니다.

### HTTP Request

`PATCH <%= config[:version] %>/user/password`

### Scopes

- `user:anonymous`

### Response Code

| Code | Description |
| ---- | ----------- |
| 204  | No Content  |

### Error Code
| Code | Message | Description |
| ---- | ------- | ----------- |
| 400 | INVALID_PASSWORD | 유효하지 않은 비밀번호 |
| 400 | SAME_PASSWORD | 이전 비밀번호와 동일한 비밀번호 |